#* ''It was dark now. The sun was nearly set, and rain was starting to fall. Kelly headed south on York Road towards the city, well fed and relaxed himself, feeling confident and ready for the night’s '''travail'''.'' {{source|{{w|Tom Clancy}}, ''{{w|Sans aucun remords|Without Remorse}}'', 1993.}}
